Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:08.59,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不要抹去心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:11.22,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不要獨自哭泣
